{"tid":737872,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Gobee.bike個創辦人賊眉賊眼，一早知佢古惑啦！","createTime":"2018-07-11T06:23:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T06:23:38.000Z","uid":148652,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ebbb31853125a06e6dd9149be425c2d65b194049","tid":737872,"uid":148652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T06:23:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/288637.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F288637.jpg&h=6124756c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGobee.bike宣布結業 拒退餘額遭用戶炮轟<br />\n<br />\n首家在本港引進共享單車服務的Gobee.bike，昨日突然宣布下周三起結束業務，用戶在一個月內可提出按金退還申請。不少用戶批評Gobee.bike不退回餘額的做法，更在facebook成立群組申訴，已有超過五百人加入。Gobee.bike行政總裁Raphael Cohen表示，香港的市場小，但共享單車公司愈來愈多，加上維修費高，公司無法賺取盈利，自去年十月一直未找到投資者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/gobee-bike宣布結業-拒退餘額遭用戶炮轟-221116371.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fgobee-bike%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD-%E6%8B%92%E9%80%80%E9%A4%98%E9%A1%8D%E9%81%AD%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E7%82%AE%E8%BD%9F-221116371.html&d=%2Fkaltkj%2F2%2BdPrSqMvx58uU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=9fb5e27c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/gobee-bike宣布結業-拒退餘額遭用戶炮轟-221116371.html</a>"}]}